content: It was used before moving to the athletes' village. Sometimes I could see national players.

The monument hall is very special...because there are many modern buildings nearby, but the simple architectural style of this monument hall is retained. It is a meaningful existence. It is a memorial to history. It is worth seeing. There are Korean Chinese, Japanese and English multilingual introduction ～

The monument is located in the corner of Guanghuamen Square, near Qingxichuan. It is a 40-year celebration of the 26th king of the Korean dynasty, Li Xi. Typical traditional Korean moth building. There is a "road mark" in the corner of the monument, which is the center point of a country.
